    • rewrite

      public PipelineAggregationBuilder rewrite​(QueryRewriteContext context) throws java.io.IOException
      Rewrites this instance based on the provided context. The returned objects will be the same instance as this if no changes during the rewrite were applied.

      The default implementation return the same instance. It should be overridden by aggregations that must load data before they can be run, particularly if that load must by asynchronous.
